---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL.replace(/\/$/, ''); // Remove trailing slash if present
---

<MainLayout title="Overview">
  <h1>AI in Digital Humanities</h1>
  <p class="text-lg text-slate-500 -mt-4 mb-8 font-sans">
    Projects, Grants, Successes & Risks (2025–2026)
  </p>

  <h2>Executive Summary</h2>

  <p>
    Artificial intelligence has transitioned from an experimental auxiliary to a core methodological
    tool across the digital humanities landscape. The period from January 2025 through March 2026
    has been defined by major grant investments—most notably <strong>Schmidt Sciences' $11 million
    HAVI program</strong>—and landmark breakthroughs in manuscript recovery and archival access.
  </p>

  <div class="not-prose my-10 p-6 bg-amber-50 border-l-4 border-amber-500 rounded-r-lg">
    <p class="text-slate-700 font-medium">
      This report surveys the current state of AI applications in humanities research, examining
      funding opportunities, technical achievements, community-centered projects, and critical
      ethical considerations.
    </p>
  </div>

  <h2>Report Sections</h2>

  <div class="not-prose grid gap-4 mt-8">
    <a href={`${base}/funding/`} class="group block p-5 bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200 hover:border-amber-400 hover:shadow-md transition-all">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-slate-100 group-hover:bg-amber-100 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-600 group-hover:text-amber-700 transition-colors">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v12m-3-2.818.879.659c1.171.879 3.07.879 4.242 0 1.172-.879 1.172-2.303 0-3.182C13.536 12.219 12.768 12 12 12c-.725 0-1.45-.22-2.003-.659-1.106-.879-1.106-2.303 0-3.182s2.9-.879 4.006 0l.415.33M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 group-hover:text-amber-700 transition-colors">I. The Major Funding Landscape</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-1">Schmidt Sciences HAVI Program, NEH grants, and the current funding climate.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href={`${base}/transcription/`} class="group block p-5 bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200 hover:border-amber-400 hover:shadow-md transition-all">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-slate-100 group-hover:bg-amber-100 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-600 group-hover:text-amber-700 transition-colors">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 14.25v-2.625a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-3.375-3.375h-1.5A1.125 1.125 0 0 1 13.5 7.125v-1.5a3.375 3.375 0 0 0-3.375-3.375H8.25m0 12.75h7.5m-7.5 3H12M10.5 2.25H5.625c-.621 0-1.125.504-1.125 1.125v17.25c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125h12.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V11.25a9 9 0 0 0-9-9Z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 group-hover:text-amber-700 transition-colors">II. Manuscript Transcription (HTR)</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-1">CoMMA Project achievements and the Transkribus platform.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href={`${base}/ancient-texts/`} class="group block p-5 bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200 hover:border-amber-400 hover:shadow-md transition-all">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-slate-100 group-hover:bg-amber-100 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-600 group-hover:text-amber-700 transition-colors">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 21v-8.25M15.75 21v-8.25M8.25 21v-8.25M3 9l9-6 9 6m-1.5 12V10.332A48.36 48.36 0 0 0 12 9.75c-2.551 0-5.056.2-7.5.582V21M3 21h18M12 6.75h.008v.008H12V6.75Z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 group-hover:text-amber-700 transition-colors">III. Ancient Text Recovery & Archaeology</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-1">DeepMind's Aeneas and the Vesuvius Challenge breakthroughs.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href={`${base}/social-justice/`} class="group block p-5 bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200 hover:border-amber-400 hover:shadow-md transition-all">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-slate-100 group-hover:bg-amber-100 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-600 group-hover:text-amber-700 transition-colors">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M18 18.72a9.094 9.094 0 0 0 3.741-.479 3 3 0 0 0-4.682-2.72m.94 3.198.001.031c0 .225-.012.447-.037.666A11.944 11.944 0 0 1 12 21c-2.17 0-4.207-.576-5.963-1.584A6.062 6.062 0 0 1 6 18.719m12 0a5.971 5.971 0 0 0-.941-3.197m0 0A5.995 5.995 0 0 0 12 12.75a5.995 5.995 0 0 0-5.058 2.772m0 0a3 3 0 0 0-4.681 2.72 8.986 8.986 0 0 0 3.74.477m.94-3.197a5.971 5.971 0 0 0-.94 3.197M15 6.75a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Zm6 3a2.25 2.25 0 1 1-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 0 1 4.5 0Zm-13.5 0a2.25 2.25 0 1 1-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 0 1 4.5 0Z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 group-hover:text-amber-700 transition-colors">IV. Social Justice & Underrepresented Communities</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-1">Community-centered AI and indigenous language revitalization.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a href={`${base}/ethics/`} class="group block p-5 bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200 hover:border-amber-400 hover:shadow-md transition-all">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-slate-100 group-hover:bg-amber-100 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-600 group-hover:text-amber-700 transition-colors">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" class="w-5 h-5">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 9v3.75m-9.303 3.376c-.866 1.5.217 3.374 1.948 3.374h14.71c1.73 0 2.813-1.874 1.948-3.374L13.949 3.378c-.866-1.5-3.032-1.5-3.898 0L2.697 16.126ZM12 15.75h.007v.008H12v-.008Z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 group-hover:text-amber-700 transition-colors">V. Ethical Risks & Critical Perspectives</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-1">Training bias, cultural flattening, and the GLAM scraping crisis.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </a>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
